Resource Profile: Decompression Sickness

Official URL: https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/StructureDefinition/DecompressionSickness Version: 0.5.4
Draft as of 2025-12-29 Computable Name: DecompressionSickness

Decompression sickness occurring during diving or altitude training

Usages:

  • This Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
